Package: emodule-mpdule
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-mpdule
Description: MPD module for Enlightenment
 An E17 module to show the MPD status in the shelf.
 
Package: emodule-net
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-net
Description: An E17 network interface monitor module
 An E17 module which monitors TX and RX events of a specified
 network device. Features are:
 - show text and/or graph
 - configure poll interval
 - choose device.
 
Package: emodule-news
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999), xdg-utils
Provides: emodule0-news
Description: The E17 new modules
 An E17 module to display feeds like Rss or Atom on the desktop.

Package: emodule-notification
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-notification
Description: E17 notification daemon
 An E17 module which provides a notification daemon for E17. It implements
 the galago specification.

