 An E17 module to display penguins on the desktop.
 
Package: emodule-photo
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-photo
Description: An E17 module for displaying pictures
 An E17 module which displays pictures in a slideshow.
 Some of the features are:
 - define mouse button to trigger action
 - actions such as set as background, show infos or open in a viewer.
 
Package: emodule-rain
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-rain
Description: An E17 module displaying rain on the desktop
 An E17 module which displays falling rainsdrops on the desktop.
 Features are:
 - display/hide clouds
 - set rain density.
 
