Package: emodule-uptime
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-uptime
Description: An E17 uptime indicator module
 An E17 module indicating the system's current uptime in a configurable
 interval.
 
Package: emodule-weather
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-weather
Description: An E17 weather module
 An E17 module displaying the current weather conditions.
 Features are:
 - choose between simple and detailed view
 - specify poll time
 - display degree in Celsius or Fahrenheit
 - choose the weather station from a menu or via ICAO Code.
 
Package: emodule-winselector
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-winselector
Description: An E17 module providing menu-based access to all windows
 An E17 module which enables access to all windows through a shelf
 button.

Package: emodule-wlan
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, enlightenment (>= 0.16.999)
Provides: emodule0-wlan
Description: An E17 WLAN monitor module
 An E17 module monitoring the link quality of a wireless network
 interface. Features are:
 - choose display as text and/or graph
 - specify the check interval.

Package: emodules-all
Architecture: any
Depends: enlightenment (>= 0.16.999), emodule-alarm, emodule-bling, emodule-calendar, emodule-cpu, emodule-deskshow, emodule-echo, emodule-efm-nav, emodule-efm-path, emodule-emu, emodule-execwatch, emodule-flame, emodule-forecasts, emodule-iiirk, emodule-language, emodule-mail, emodule-mem, emodule-mixer, emodule-moon, emodule-mpdule, emodule-net, emodule-news, emodule-notification, emodule-penguins, emodule-photo, emodule-rain, emodule-screenshot, emodule-slideshow, emodule-snow, emodule-taskbar, emodule-tclock, emodule-uptime, emodule-weather, emodule-winselector, emodule-wlan
Provides: emodules0-all, e17-modules
Description: A dummy package for installing all modules for E17
 This package will install all available modules.
